00:17:07.519 --> 00:17:11.519
In the first century, it existed among true Christians.

00:17:11.519 --> 00:17:14.519
Christians in Jerusalem and in the Roman province Judea

00:17:14.519 --> 00:17:16.519
faced very difficult times.

00:17:16.519 --> 00:17:22.519
Jesus warned them that the Roman armies would insert the city and attack it.

00:17:22.519 --> 00:17:27.519
